            <h1 id="rightframe_2_articleTitle" class="mockH2">Opening up open data: An interview with Tim O’Reilly</h1>
            <h2 id="rightframe_2_articleDescription" class="grayNote large">The tech entrepreneur, author, and investor looks at how open data is becoming a critical tool for business and government, as well as what needs to be done for it to be more effective.</h2>
            <span class="silverNote small"><span id="rightframe_2_articleDate" class="bold">January 2014</span>
                <span id="rightframe_2_articleAuthors"></span></span>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="content clearfix">
        <div class="leftInteriorTwoColumn page">
        <div class="downloadBarWrapper">
            
            </div>
            <div id="rightframe_2_articleBody" class="container article">
    <script language="JavaScript" type="text/javascript">
        
